="icon-bar"></span> </button> <a class="navbar-brand" href="http://www.s3-international.com">S3International</a> </div><div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="bs-example-navbar-collapse-1"> <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right"> <li> <a href="#showroom">About Us</a> </li><li> <a href="#brands">Our Brands</a> </li><li> <a href="#team">Our Team</a> </li><li> <a href="contact.php">Contact</a> </li></ul> </div></div></nav> <div class="intro-header img-responsive"> <div class="container"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-lg-12 dark_opacity"> <div class="intro-message"> <img class="main-logo" src="img/S3logo.png"> <hr class="intro-divider"> <ul class="list-inline intro-social-buttons"> <li> <a href="#aboutus" class="btn btn-default btn-lg"> <span class="network-name">About Us</span> </a> </li><li> <a href="#brands" class="btn btn-default btn-lg"> <span class="network-name">Our Brands</span> </a> </li><li> <a href="#team" class="btn btn-default btn-lg"><span class="network-name">Our Team</span></a> </li></ul> </div></div></div></div></div><section class="bg1"> <div id="aboutus" class="content-section-b"> <div class="container"> <h1>About S3International</h1> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-6"> <div class="caption aboutS3"> <h3>Providing the very best Sales Service Solutions in tactical, outdoor, and cycling markets for the APAC region.</h3> <p class="">S3International is a full service sales and distribution agency representing major U.S. and European manufacturers in Asia Pacific - APAC. Our primary role is to represent the manufacturer as an extension of their company sales team. We are fully authorized and sanctioned by the manufacturers as their APAC sales representatives.</p><p>S3International was founded on the premise that many companies do not have sales representation in APAC nor do they have the resources to actively develop this unique market segment. We are able to use our experience and local presence to provide a foundation for establishing and growing major brands regionally. The key to our success is to provide excellent <em>Sales Service Solutions</em> </p></div></div><div class="col-md-6 col-sm-4"> <img class="map" style="max-width: 100%; padding-top: 50px;" src="img/asia.png"> </div></div><div class="row sss "> <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4"> <div class="text-center"> <i class="fa fa-handshake-o fa-5x"></i> <h2>Sales</h2> <div class="text-left"> <ul> <li>Provide regional coverage with multiple sales representatives</li><li>Establish annual sales quotas for dealers and distributors</li><li>Develop strategic sales channels</li><li>Increase revenue and market share</li><li>Create government tender specifications</li><li>Order configuration</li><li>Brand awareness</li></ul> </div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4"> <div class="text-center"> <i class="fa fa-users fa-5x"></i> <h2>Service</h2> <div class="text-left"> <ul> <li>Develop and maintain strong partner relationships</li><li>Real-time customer interaction</li><li>Consistent sales calls to key accounts</li><li>Face-to-face product training</li><li>Assist with warranty and after sales service</li><li>Trade show management and participation</li><li>Manage Department of State and Commerce Department requirements</li></ul> </div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4"> <div class="text-center"> <i class="fa fa-lightbulb-o fa-5x"></i> <h2>Solutions</h2> <div class="text-left"> <ul> <li>Single source of information</li><li>Unbiased analysis of accounts, activities and competitors</li><li>Seamless integration between manufacturer, distributor and end-user</li></ul> </div></div></div></div></div></div></section> <section class="bg2"> <div id="brands" class="content-section-a"> <div class="container center-anchor"> <h1>Our Brands</h1> <ul class="list-inline intro-social-buttons"> <li> <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-lg" data-mixitup-control data-filter="all">All</button> </li><li> <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-lg" data-mixitup-control data-filter=".tactical">Tactical</button> </li><li> <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-lg" data-mixitup-control data-filter=".bike-outdoor">Bike/Outdoor</button> </li></ul> <div class="row brand-list"> <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4 mix tactical"> <a class="thumbnail" href="#SFModal" role="button" data-toggle="modal"> <img src="img/logoedits/surefire.png"> </a> <div id="SFModal" class="modal fade" role="dialog"> <div class="modal-dialog"> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-header"> <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button> <h4 class="modal-title">SUREFIRE</h4> </div><div class="modal-body"> <p>Manufacturer of flashlights, headlamps, weapon lights, suppressors, and hearing protection for the military, law enforcement, shooting sports and home defense industries.</p><h4 class="modallisttitle">S3International represents SUREFIRE in the following countries:</h4> <ul class="modallist"> <li>Bangladesh</li><li>Borneo</li><li>Myanmar (Burma)</li><li>Brunei</li><li>Cambodia</li><li>Fiji</li><li>Indonesia</li><li>Laos</li><li>Malaysia</li><li>New Guinea</li><li>Singapore</li><li>Solomon Islands</li><li>Tonga</li><li>India</li><li>Sri Lanka</li><li>Nepal</li><li>Bhutan</li><li>Thailand</li><li>Vietnam</li><li>Australia</li><li>New Zealand</li></ul> <img style="max-width: 100%; " src="img/modalimgs/surefiremodal.jpg"></img> </div><div class="modal-footer"> <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button> </div></div></div></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4 mix tactical"> <a class="thumbnail" href="#511Modal" role="button" data-toggle="modal"> <img src="img/logoedits/511.png"> </a> <div id="511Modal" class="modal fade" role="dialog"> <div class="modal-dialog"> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-header"> <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button> <h4 class="modal-title">5.11 Tactical Equipment</h4> </div><div class="modal-body"> <p>Manufacturer of tactical clothing, uniforms, outerwear and tactical gear for military, law enforcement, and firefighting professionals.</p><h4 class="modallisttitle">S3International represents 5.11 Tactical in the following countries:</h4> <ul class="modallist"> <li>Singapore</li><li>Vietnam</li><li>Bangladesh</li></ul> <img style="max-width: 100%; " src="img/modalimgs/511modal.jpg"></img> </div><div class="modal-footer"> <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button> </div></div></div></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4 mix tactical"> <a class="thumbnail" href="#ASPModal" role="button" data-toggle="modal"> <img src="img/logoedits/asp.png"> </a> <div id="ASPModal" class="modal fade" role="dialog"> <div class="modal-dialog"> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-header"> <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button> <h4 class="modal-title">ASP - Armament Systems and Procedures</h4> </div><div class="modal-body"> <p>Armament Systems and Procedures, Inc. is a defensive compliance weapons manufacturer providing equipment to law enforcement and private security companies to include batons, restraints, and lighting.</p><h4 class="modallisttitle">S3International represents ASP in the following countries:</h4> <ul class="modallist"> <li>Australia</li><li>Bangladesh</li><li>Borneo</li><li>Brunei</li><li>Cambodia</li><li>China</li><li>Fiji</li><li>Hong Kong</li><li>India</li><li>Indonesia</li><li>Japan</li><li>Laos</li><li>Macau</li><li>Malaysia</li><li>Mongolia</li><li>Myanmar (Burma)</li><li>Nepal</li><li>New Guinea</li><li>New Zealand</li><li>Pakistan</li><li>Philippines</li><li>Singapore</li><li>Solomon Islands</li><li>South Korea</li><li>Sri Lanka</li><li>Taiwan</li><li>Thailand</li><li>Tonga</li><li>Vietnam</li></ul> <img style="max-width: 100%; " src="img/modalimgs/aspmodal.jpg"></img> </div><div class="modal-footer"> <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button> </div></div></div></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4 mix tactical"> <a class="thumbnail" href="#TWModal" role="button" data-toggle="modal"> <img src="img/logoedits/teamwendy.png"> </a> <div id="TWModal" class="modal fade" role="dialog"> <div class="modal-dialog"> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-header"> <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button> <h4 class="modal-title">Team Wendy</h4> </div><div class="modal-body"> <p>Manufacturer of ballistic helmets, helmet liners and accessories for military, law enforcement, and search and rescue.</p><h4 class="modallisttitle">S3International represents Team Wendy in the following countries:</h4> <ul class="modallist"> <li>Brunei</li><li>Cambodia</li><li>China</li><li>Hong Kong</li><li>Indonesia</li><li>Japan</li><li>Laos</li><li>Macau</li><li>Malaysia</li><li>Mongolia</li><li>Myanmar (Burma)</li><li>Nepal</li><li>Philippines</li><li>Singapore</li><li>Sri Lanka</li><li>Taiwan</li><li>Thailand</li><li>Vietnam</li></ul> <img style="max-width: 100%; " src="img/modalimgs/teamwendymodal.jpg"></img> </div><div class="modal-footer"> <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button> </div></div></div></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4 mix tactical"> <a class="thumbnail" href="#SMITHModal" role="button" data-toggle="modal"> <img src="img/logoedits/smithelitelogo.png"> </a> <div id="SMITHModal" class="modal fade" role="dialog"> <div class="modal-dialog"> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-header"> <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button> <h4 class="modal-title">SMITH ELITE</h4> </div><div class="modal-body"> <p>Manufacturer of protective eyewear, sunglasses, goggles, replacement lenses and accessories.</p><h4 class="modallisttitle">S3International represents SMITH Elite in the following countries:</h4> <ul class="modallist"> <li>Australia</li><li>Bangladesh</li><li>Borneo</li><li>Brunei</l